scenes.description: Performance of the song 'Étude wa 1 Kyoku Dake' by Moona Hoshinova, Hakos Baelz, Anya Melfissa, and Kureiji Ollie.
Moona Hoshinova delivers an MC section, thanking the audience and talking about her 5th anniversary and the 3D live preparation.
Moona introduces her 'Birthday Celebration 2025' merchandise set, adopting an announcer persona.

subtitles.english: Always more, an étude just for me.

subtitles.original: えー えー えー あー
subtitles.english: Eh eh eh ah...
